	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">It only worked when I removed that CLI and placed it outside of the NMI routine, before the NMI routine runs for the first time.</div>
<br />You are aware that RTI restores the status flags (including I) to what it was before NMI was entered, right? I'm guessing that's your problem.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
